      <head>Alpenhaus Fluchthorn</head>
      <div>

        <p>Restaurant, guesthouse, later hotel, in <ref cRef="entity-002292">Galtür</ref>, in the
          Austrian Tyrol. </p>

        <p>The Alpenhaus Fluchthorn was acquired by the Galtür <ref cRef="entity-002925">Türtscher
            family</ref> at the beginning of the 1920s. <ref cRef="entity-000903">Adolf
            Türtscher</ref> took over the proprietorship and built it up into a full-scale
          hotel.</p>

      </div>


      <div>
        <head>The Alpenhaus Fluchthorn and the Schenkers</head>

        <p>Heinrich and Jeanette Schenker stayed at the Alpenhaus Fluchthorn for the summer
          vacations of 1921, 1922, 1923, and 1924. </p>

      </div>

